        {
            "id": 6326632,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 特許通訊(CHTR-US)大漲5.02%，報191.98美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>特許通訊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CHTR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CHTR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CHTR-US</a>)截至台北時間30日04:57股價上漲9.17美元，報191.98美元，漲幅5.02%，成交量3,227,567（股），盤中最高價191.98美元、最低價180.38美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.11%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.13%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.74%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.11%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>特許通訊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CHTR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CHTR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CHTR-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-2.34%</li> <li>近 1 月：-11.67%</li> <li>近 3 月：-26.47%</li> <li>近 6 月：-38.65%</li> <li>今年以來：-12.34%</li></ul></section></main>",
