            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Applovin Corp - Class A(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:APP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/APP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">APP-US</a>)截至台北時間30日04:56股價上漲27.12美元，報569.48美元，漲幅5%，成交量4,627,425（股），盤中最高價569.51美元、最低價542.00美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.11%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.13%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.76%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.1%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Applovin Corp - Class A(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:APP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/APP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">APP-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+2.07%</li> <li>近 1 月：-23.9%</li> <li>近 3 月：-13.28%</li> <li>近 6 月：+46.53%</li> <li>今年以來：-19.33%</li></ul></section></main>",
